## AI Tool Plan

### Label stress-testing
Give Claude my label definitions and ask it to generate
10 posts at the boundary between `hot_take` and `analysis`.
If I can't classify them cleanly, tighten definitions
before annotating.

### Annotation assistance
Use an LLM to pre-label batches of 20-30 examples using
my label definitions as a system prompt. Review and correct
every single pre-assigned label. Flag pre-labeled examples
in a `prelabeled` column in the CSV.

### Failure analysis
After training, paste wrong predictions into Claude and ask
it to identify common patterns. Verify each pattern myself
before including it in the report.
